## Paperback print settings (must match the generated files)
- **Trim size:** {{ "%g"|format(cfg.trim_w) }} x {{ "%g"|format(cfg.trim_h) }} in
{%- if cfg.book_type in ("picture", "concept") %}
- **Interior:** Standard Color (full-colour illustrations)
- **Paper:** White — ⚠ select white; the spine width ({{ spine }}in) was computed for white/colour stock.
{%- else %}
- **Interior:** Black & white
- **Paper:** Cream  — ⚠ must select cream; the spine width ({{ spine }}in) was computed for cream stock. White paper is thinner and KDP will reject the cover.
{%- endif %}
- **Bleed (interior):** No Bleed — the interior PDF is exactly {{ "%g"|format(cfg.trim_w) }}x{{ "%g"|format(cfg.trim_h) }} with margins (no edge-to-edge images).
- **Cover finish:** Matte (recommended for the soft watercolor art; free choice, doesn't affect the file).
- **ISBN:** Get a free KDP ISBN (KDP-only is fine).{% if cfg.makes_ebook %} The eBook needs **no ISBN** (Amazon assigns an ASIN).{% endif %}
- **In Print Previewer:** confirm the wraparound lines up and the **back-cover blurb clears the barcode** box (lower-right of the back cover).

